                     <interp inst="t18370508-1231-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">GUILTY</hi>. Aged 16.—Of stealing under the value of £5.<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury and Prosecutor</hi>.</rs>—
